{"tid":2036530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日一定要出 唔好俾五毛帶失敗風唔出","createTime":"2020-05-26T13:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T13:49:15.000Z","uid":248966,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a08cf5e4cf1b68144c4c3a18f5f11fca30464c6","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"第一次出post，不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲狗佈防係癲咗好多，但國安法、國歌法都唔出嘅，即係你已經放棄咗街頭抗爭，已經放棄咗爭取民主同公義。唔想放棄嘅手足，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚早啲訓</span></strong></span>，養足精神打大佬。<br />\n<br />\n其實聽日可以做到好多嘢，怕風險大咪塞下鐵、可以嘅black bloc組埋哨塞馬路（紅隧、東隧交俾車手手足）。大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定要記得睇時間</strong></span></span>，8、9點左右都仲未塞到就要吹大雞入港島。<br />\n<br />\n港島一定要聚到人！入唔到金環咪入<span style=\"color: red;\">中環、灣仔</span>，再唔得咪<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣、天后</span>，總之港島人要夠多，盡量包圍到去立法會嘅路。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好俾其他人帶到風向</span></span>，如果狗多就唔出，咁我幾肯定以後唔會再有街頭抗爭，香港都可以正式宣佈玩撚完。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨想同我地攬炒，我地咪奉陪到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家肯抗爭仲有一絲希望。<span style=\"color: red;\">總之聽日咩方法都要試下</span>，盡做！<br />\n<br />\n最後，大家萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人冇事先係世界冠軍。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立，唯一出路</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"09e632804ed56cb14ee983fbb2f0c4c4606f4b4e","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"2ee9db6a1ec087fc0ee6424c99df6ad632f2279c","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"707e59f7535139bc7b46e00f528b47b914f6a9cc","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"7e206169d52b62bbc86ac953f0c01b891ea82c6a","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"de20641134e377d19599f7521f0a01441cb78b2f","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"3fae303b517f3d0506596d44b4ec081426791ebd","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"d6f7c952eb61a6477728edcfbeee860f9b0bc0fd","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"a35385c763a0e89c5972773e79fd24999ab9b476","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"2c35563f598920262a7b8f1acbc306383a475556","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"ef2d6fdf3cb11c9f7ae3cefd532f47978599c1b0","tid":2036530,"uid":248966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"自推x10"}]}